  "A city's drinking water supply comes from a river that passes through agricultural and industrial areas upstream. After a drought, water quality deteriorates significantly. The city must choose between building a new reservoir, purchasing water from a neighboring district, or improving its treatment plant. This decision requires what type of assessment?": "",
